name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Worms Zone a Slithery Snake online

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Worms Zone is an online game with a dynamic storyline. Start growing your worm right now. play and enjoy the game.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Worms Zone a Slithery Snake online is available in the chrome web store just install it and play Worms Zone a Slithery Snake online game.


Worms Zone a Slithery Snake is a .io game in which you have to collect as much food as possible with your snake. The aim is to make your snake grow as big as possible and rise to the top of the leaderboard. Slither through the multiplayer arena and try to eat other players to grow bigger even faster.
